        "subject": "LU-410 obdfilter: Allocate contigous pages to avoid fragmented IO.",
        "message": "LU-410 obdfilter: Allocate contigous pages to avoid fragmented IO.\n\nAllocate contiguous pages for niobuf can help to\navoid fragmented IO, if the backend driver does not\nextend its MAX_HW_SEGMENTS to 256, which is necessary\nfor 1M IO.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ib74fcbfd0284ae2ea46b928012e4ebc2065d5fd2\n"
